{"tid":1418983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國正式將中國列為匯率操縱國","createTime":"2019-08-05T22:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:23:06.000Z","uid":202262,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d180eb4db2bf75a23e8a0976b335f182bfd2b986","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:35:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472962-20190806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472962-20190806.htm&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=1e9f83d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472962-20190806.htm&h=59149c16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472962-20190806.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n人民幣匯率自2008年來，首度跌穿七算的心理關口後，美國財政部正式將中國列為匯率操縱國。<br />\n<br />\n財政部發表聲明，批評中國在中美貿易戰升溫時，削弱人民幣匯率，財長努欽在總統特朗普的支持下，確認中國為匯率操縱國，努欽將與國際貨幣基金組織商討，消除中國最新行動帶來的不公平競爭優勢。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前在社交網站貼文，指中國讓他們的貨幣貶值到歷史低位，這些叫「操縱匯率」，是嚴重違規。<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行行長易綱說，8月以來很多貨幣兌美元貶值，人民幣匯率亦受一定程度影響，波動是市場驅動及決定，強調中國堅持市場決定的匯率制度，不搞競爭性貶值，不將匯率用於競爭目的，亦不會將匯率作為應對貿易爭端等的工具。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c6ad0e15c7e20361d4bc4f768db557ce4df209","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:37:23.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"17aebcbcb4e8bb85ca40aef03788427fb1d76f09","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:37:33.000Z","msg":"壹"},{"pid":"2bd2e37d528682cdaeaaaebfdd6926ce62b309a4","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:37:50.000Z","msg":"貳"},{"pid":"f83e824b886c4533eb6fc60cd902eba72c5ac1f6","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:38:08.000Z","msg":"叁"},{"pid":"12f7b9a307830cbbd58e60a850201a71e980d1f5","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:38:20.000Z","msg":"肆"},{"pid":"31e57da319244f60954f0e81d2cd93f7e42bdbe7","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:38:39.000Z","msg":"伍"},{"pid":"a12b573a5690a35e21584bcb1990e04424a734fb","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"陸"},{"pid":"6d841f50b06901e01159d8a91fed4e2104297c5e","tid":1418983,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:39:04.000Z","msg":"柒"},{"pid":"c707ef293c47b578941bfb94e91d5721e52d653f","tid":1418983,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypFgj2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypFgj2X.jpg&h=4d03816c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a61ce2aad399889181423f59ea9a76f541cfb2ce","tid":1418983,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:40:24.000Z","msg":"行動升級"},{"pid":"f48c3948413629fc965e81b1ceb9fb5c06b3d0cc","tid":1418983,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:42:28.000Z","msg":"匯率操縱國其實有咩問題？<br />\n理科人不明白"},{"pid":"717fe3f2fc416072ed05bc4b028413fa202eb6a4","tid":1418983,"uid":167937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f48c3948413629fc965e81b1ceb9fb5c06b3d0cc","tid":1418983,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:42:28.000Z","msg":"匯率操縱國其實有咩問題？<br />\n理科人不明白"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T22:48:37.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n點解調低匯率反而有好處？"},{"pid":"f800df193320272a9e1778d1cdc8ac1d521652c3","tid":1418983,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f48c3948413629fc965